      "message": "this seems odd.\n\nAre you converting \\ to / to deal with windows paths? If so, you probably should be looking at File.separator to determine if it should be replaced. Technically, \\ is a valid character in a unix filename.\n\nIf not dealing with windows paths, please add comments to say why you're doing this. JavaDocs comments are always welcome irregardless.",
